PEMOTE: Possessive emote

Syntax: pemote <text>

DESCRIPTION:
  Sends a possessive emote to the room. Your character's name is
  displayed followed by "'s" and then your text.

EXAMPLE:
  pemote sword hums with psionic energy.
  (room sees: Bob's sword hums with psionic energy.)

  pemote eyes narrow with suspicion.
  (room sees: Bob's eyes narrow with suspicion.)

COST:
  7 magic points for characters under level 20. Free for level 20
  and above.

SEE ALSO: emote, say, whisper, yell
